/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
19 December 2022	navsp1	Initial creation - TFS ChangeRequest 55580: EUP - Inspection App checks - Interface and MTN changes

*/

vars

begin
	return inheritMethod(json, expectErrors);

epilog

end;</source>
