        <source>wsRESTDeleteReleaseRequest(_incomingJson, _urlParams : String; _expectErrors : Boolean): String;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date			Who		Reason
07 April 2023	navak20	Task 57526: CUX - MTN-EDBIC - 100 - Process Release Request - GET Unit Test
05 August 2024	navmd1	TFS 65132 Refactor to allow urlParameters to be passed

