        <source>wsRESTGetProformaAmount(_loginString: String; _queryParamString: String; _response: String io; _totalAmount : Decimal io; _expectFailure: Boolean): String;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
02/05/2024	navkc1 CR63397  Task 63398: Jade - New REST API getProformaAmountForVoyage
29-Oct-2025	navtr3 MTN-36371 [MasterTerminalAPI] Verbose Unauthenticated Error Objects Expose API Schema
